<![CDATA[<div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},</div><div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br></div><div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><div><b>Your insurance policy&nbsp;<i>[policy number]</i>&nbsp;is due to expire on&nbsp;<i>[expiry date]</i>.</b></div><div><br></div><div>If you wish to renew your business insurance policy, you can contact us on&nbsp;<b>01242 808740</b>&nbsp;between the hours&nbsp;<b>8:00am – 5:30pm Monday-Friday</b>&nbsp;and our team will complete your purchase over the phone.</div><div><br></div><div><font size="4"><b>We will beat any like for like quote</b></font></div><div>Our&nbsp;<a href="https://go.kingsbridge.co.uk/PL-MRR-0225">Price Promise</a>&nbsp;means that if you find like-for-like cover elsewhere at a lower price, we will beat the quote. Terms and conditions apply.</div><div><br></div><div>We hope you find our policy suits all your business needs and we look forward to hearing from you.</div><b><br></b></div><div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="background-color: white;">Kind regards,<br></span><span style="background-color: white;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="background-color: white;">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="background-color: white;"><br>E:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk" style="background-color: white; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</a><br><span style="background-color: white;">T: 01242 808 740</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
